says suspiciously, "Yah, what's going on here?!" 

ooC: I leave for university in several days, so I'm going to be 
dropping many characters. I'll have to decided which ones I'll keep 
and which I won't, but I'm pretty busy right now so that'll have to 
wait. I've been mostly inactive lately, and I'm not sure how long it 
will take me to get back online, so don't expect to hear from me 
too often.
